dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"加速染紅 步亞視後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d95f0b543c6b9484da78951bf89eb7144c0a223","tid":1833783,"uid":236646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人唔知係官媒呀。賣唔賣一樣咁垃圾"},{"pid":"4fe177f92c6ac4c0ce8f26addb37f1ee3683bed5","tid":1833783,"uid":272652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"咁實變海狗公園，執硬"},{"pid":"639a229da647de0b60269a92769ff50bfcaf3dc1","tid":1833783,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"迫人退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05aab9771b38fd5c011f032489b5900599dc1c4b","tid":1833783,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"CCTVB"},{"pid":"3fe4bbcbd43ee7092e5f0c93896fe1649d91397d","tid":1833783,"uid":67551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad6d904b110b1e0490ed2e6fabe556579f9b5fa","tid":1833783,"uid":18477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"被退休<br />\n翻版馬雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faac6c651972055f4470070a261e1778f768a0b","tid":1833783,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334a1192266e028faa8645689dc51b89a98cbc4a","tid":1833783,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-0